DESCRIPTION:Join us on Wednesday\, April 29\, from 4 - 7 PM at Whispering Vine South Creek for a tasting featuring Caymus.\nTasting Fee: $35 per person (Buy a bottle from the tasting\, get the tasting fee refunded.)\nFeatured Wines:\n- Caymus California Cabernet Sauvignon 2023 – $44.99\, Winery $55 – Introduced by Caymus Vineyards with the 2021 vintage\, this wine is a California-appellation Cabernet Sauvignon - supple\, dark and rich\, bearing the signature hallmarks of Caymus.\n- Red Schooner by Caymus Voyage 12 – $29.99 – Grapes for this Malbec are grown in the Andes Mountains of Argentina\, then chilled and transported by ocean voyage to Caymus\, where we use our winemaking techniques to create a style that is dense\, dark and supple.\n- Red Schooner by Caymus Transit No. 2 – $39.99\, Winery $50 – Red Schooner's new "Red Wine of the World\," this red blend is sourced from famed regions of southern Australia\, the Barossa Valley and McLaren Vale.\n- Bonanza by Chuck Wagner The Vinekeeper Cabernet Sauvignon – $29.99 – Beautifully balanced - rich\, fruit-driven\, round and ripe.\nCome explore Caymus and find your favorite bottle. Buy a bottle from the tasting and your fee is refunded.
LOCATION:85 Foothill Rd Ste 1 Reno\, NV 89511
SUMMARY:Caymus Tasting at South Creek
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR